Organically grown across asset classes 






From our founding, we’ve held to the conviction that there is a different way for an investment firm to create value.












Our Businesses
 Private Equity
 Credit
 Public Equity
 Venture
 Strategic Alternatives








Every new business we’ve hatched came about because a talented person had the idea to apply our unique investing approach to another asset class. This has helped us preserve our unique culture and it has driven great synergy across our global platform.








From Bain Capital Private Equity’s founding in 1984, our team has partnered closely with management teams to provide the strategic resources that build great companies and help them thrive.








Our credit team applies its global reach and approach to invest up and down the capital structure and across the full spectrum of credit strategies.








Our public equity team applies deep domain expertise and a long-term perspective to identify compelling opportunities globally, investing in both publicly-traded and pre-IPO companies.








Our ventures team provides capital for seed through growth equity investments, and we bring a nuanced understanding of markets and unique global network to our long-term partnerships with disruptive B2B founders.








Leveraging the breadth and scale of our shared platform, we invest in a diverse set of strategies that capture cross-asset class opportunities in strategic areas of focus.









